    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce an exhilarating 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. This example has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul, including a high-flow water pump and aluminum radiator. The suspension geometry is maintained with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust and the compression across all six cylinders is consistent. A true driver's specification for the purist seeking analog feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
